#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:18
msgid ""
"Git push to branch\n"
"       ↓\n"
"GitHub Actions workflow\n"
"(.github/workflows/azure-static-web-apps.yml)\n"
"       ↓\n"
"npm ci  →  npm run build\n"
"       ↓\n"
"Azure Static Web Apps deployment\n"
"       ↓\n"
"https://cpsv-editor.open-regels.nl  (main)\n"
"https://acc.cpsv-editor.open-regels.nl  (acc)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:32
