#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:47
msgid "Azure Static Web Apps"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:49
msgid ""
"The application is deployed as a static site. No server-side rendering is "
"involved. The build output is the `build/` directory produced by `npm run "
"build` (Create React App)."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:51
msgid ""
"Configuration for routing and CORS is in `staticwebapp.config.json` at the "
"repository root."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:55
msgid "Environment variables"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:57
msgid ""
"The frontend has no required environment variables for basic operation. The "
"TriplyDB base URL, account, dataset, and API token are entered by the user "
"at runtime and stored in browser localStorage."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment.md:59
msgid ""
"If the optional backend proxy is deployed, its URL can be configured — see "
"the backend documentation in the Linked Data Explorer repository."
msgstr ""
